    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean and presents well, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches from normal use. Inside, the cabin is tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery, and all features are fully functional. It drives smoothly and is mechanically sound, making it an excellent choice for someone wanting a reliable, ready-to-drive car.",
