    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a functional and spirited vehicle perfect for someone looking for value. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a reliable car at an accessible price point while you add your own personal touch!",
